            <TextView
                android:id="@+id/textView2"
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                android:text="ASIAWRITERS"
                android:textColor="#de521f"
                android:textSize="20dp"
                android:textStyle="bold" />

            <TextView
                android:id="@+id/textView3"
                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal"
                android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                android:text=" 1. We are a professional writing service providing online writing jobs for talented freelance writers who want to get writer jobs. \n 2. Online writing jobs that can be taken by a freelance writer anywhere and at any time. \n 3. Each freelance writer can take orders on their own schedule and choose the subjects up to their interest among a wide variety of writing assignments. \n 4. We guarantee our freelance writers bonuses for their writer employment. \n 5. Our freelance writers have great career opportunities and a constant flow of orders to perform each day. \n 6. Reliable 24/7 support for freelance writers. \n 7. Freelance writing opportunities for experienced and talented freelance writers in India, China, Pakistan and throughout Asia."
